	- `NTGrpcClient.dll`
	- `Grpc.Core.dll`, `Grpc.Core.Api.dll`
	- `Google.Protobuf.dll`
	- `System.Text.Json.dll`
	- `grpc_csharp_ext.x64.dll` (x64 NinjaTrader)
